name: The Horrible Space Calamari From Elva 7
description: Space log 569-MW01827 .. captain turin here ..look ..all I know is we got a distress call from an abandoned space station somewhere around elva7 in the orion galaxy. what we found was this horrible hideous squid looking thing plastered in human eyeballs.. and smelled like shit with a side burning hair !! slim was able to get a snap of this monstrosity with his drone while cortez got two shots off before the thing fucking devoured him. Limited edition digital art piece by OsiRisORion
